6.7 How to Read

273
00:24:50.738 --> 00:24:54.800
6.7.0 How to choose books — see "0.

274
00:24:54.800 --> 00:25:00.813
Feasibility analysis of feasibility 到 spot-read 到 read what you don't know 到 read seriously on demand

275
00:25:00.813 --> 00:25:03.988
6.7.1 Read for Joy.

276
00:25:03.988 --> 00:25:05.925
Read for Learning.

277
